data.eml:eml: Syllidae (Annelida, Polychaeta) from the Caribbean coast of Venezuela

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Linero-Arana, Ildefonso, Diaz Diaz, Oscarn (2011): Syllidae (Annelida, Polychaeta) from the Caribbean coast of Venezuela. ZooKeys 117: 1-28, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.117.858, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.117.858
